        "level": 1,
        "html": "<!-- header 2 -->\r\n<h2>3.5 Customer Search</h2>\r\n\r\n<!-- paragraph -->\r\n<p>\r\n\tThis screen enables a user to search customer from the customers record. \r\n    The user can input from any of the input fields and it would display the customer's information based on that input.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<!-- centered image -->\r\n<center><img src=\"images/customersearch.png\"></img></center>\r\n\r\n<!-- centered and italic -->\r\n<center><i>The customer search screen</i></center>\r\n\r\n"
